{"tid":1219221,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"達狗教你點做人，好心你件柒碌胎屎就學吓啦","createTime":"2019-06-13T18:28:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T19:12:44.000Z","uid":61383,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8778b1b8c93a52a68f7dc3d7a0079e59b3def28f","tid":1219221,"uid":61383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:28:53.000Z","msg":"達狗讀書多深知禍從口出講多錯多呢啲道理，所以由今年64唔出聲，甚至反修例去到612都唔表態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完美世界之類既廣告繼續播，由得你班傻仔走住嚟屌，但係都冇畀位你地入到，直至13號凌晨仲彈出又彈入喺facebook求其講句野再潛返去地核撚你班haters一獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />facebook留言照舊有一班腦殘死忠護駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n柒碌toyz EQ低，俾聊天室釣兩野就發撚曬癲亂咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己又唔留意時事連屋企發生咩事都唔去了解，喺台灣我唔信落7仔或者其他便利店會見唔到報紙賣緊咩掛，反修例威示正正就係90後同00後佔大多數，亦都係你主要既觀眾源，以為講幾句道歉就冇事其實你呢獲永不翻身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎佢兩條友比達狗個底係，而條柒碌個底花撚到暈，鐘培生都教唔到你做人真係可惜，如果連今次英皇都炒撚埋你就真係精彩，本性難移<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我冇話達狗唔抵屌，呢件事又證明讀書多其實會學到點做人，唔好再畀藉口自己唔讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2d4c274aa7ca03efa6c45dc0583b41997a7283","tid":1219221,"uid":61383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e54e814b3884b6295d4773b8328b185b249b1786","tid":1219221,"uid":61383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:30:27.000Z","msg":"pish到柒碌見到"},{"pid":"240fadb9c35d5452f899f2a7d96e66d447d87272","tid":1219221,"uid":253631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T18:33:32.000Z","msg":"樓豬一針見血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class